      <title>里约热内卢在狂欢节前几天宣布登革热卫生紧急状态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-02-05/rio-de-janeiro-has-declared-a-dengue-health-emergency-days-before-carnival-is-due-to-start</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里约热内卢（美联社）——里约热内卢周一宣布，由于爆发蚊媒登革热，该市宣布进入公共卫生紧急状态，就在巴西各地狂欢节庆祝活动开始前几天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-02-05/rio-de-janeiro-has-declared-a-dengue-health-emergency-days-before-carnival-is-due-to-start</guid>
